Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:06.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It happened long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.06,0:00:10.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,On a night just like tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Within this very forest
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:19.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Beneath a full moon's light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.77,0:00:23.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She's called a necromancer
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.06,0:00:27.41,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But what she does is worse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,For death she does not bring
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:36.31,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But instead eternal curse
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:42.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She hides within the forest, the sunlight is her bane
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:46.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She travels on these pathways looking out for easy prey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you are so unlucky, you'll meet her face to face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.95,0:00:53.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if you don't act quickly then you surely won't escape
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.34,0:00:56.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You'll find yourself enveloped, and unable to move
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.73,0:00:59.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You're caught within her magic and now surely you are doomed
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.20,0:01:03.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Her eyes will flare up brightly the spell is now complete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:06.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And before you stands your skeleton as you're a blob of meat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:10.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blonde Spooky Bone Stealer, monster that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.45,0:01:13.63,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your actions are unnerving, your motives are bizarre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:17.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blonde Spooky Bone Stealer in the Everfree
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:20.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She wants to steal the skeleton inside of you and me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.27,0:01:36.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh, sure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:37.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now hold on, girls
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.70,0:01:38.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There might be something to this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.34,0:01:39.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Pinkie!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.98,0:01:40.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Yes, hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.48,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Fairytales are fleeting, and rumors come and go
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.77,0:01:47.95,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Not every story's meaningless and surely we should know
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.20,0:01:51.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,That stories have a reason, causation and a source
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.63,0:01:53.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And just what are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well that she's real, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.06,0:01:58.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I know it may seem crazy, but what if Pinkie's right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:01.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This forest, after all, is home to many evil frights~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:05.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If she is truly out there, and wants to steal our bones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then we must stand together, and not run off alone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:10.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Now hold it right there mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:11.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Your words are falling short
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:13.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,This pony's just a rumor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:15.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A claim with no support!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:17.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if this mare were re-al
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.34,0:02:18.66,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Then somepony would say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.09,0:02:20.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Unless she's so efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.73,0:02:22.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Nopony gets away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.81,0:02:24.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,It's gonna take more than THAT to scare us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.34,0:02:25.84,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Right, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.27,0:02:27.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Why is she doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.02,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you asked
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.34,0:02:32.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She seeks to build an army, of spooky scary bones
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:35.81,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,A skeleton battalion, that's under her control
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:39.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if she gets the numbers, Equestria is next
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.66,0:02:42.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And ponykind will falter as the skeletons oppress
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.09,0:02:46.16,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She stumbles and she shambles, along these very paths
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:49.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Awaiting further victims, to fall within her grasp
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:53.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,If you go out alone, you may end up her prey
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,"But how do we avoid her?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.84,0:02:56.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well for that you simply say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blonde Spooky Bone Stealer stay you far away
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:03.38,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Begone with your subjection, or face the light of day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.70,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Blonde Spooky Bone Stealer don't you dare pursue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:10.13,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And curse you down to Tartarus for what you try to do
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.59,0:03:25.20,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh come on, girls
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.34,0:03:26.91,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,You can't honestly be buying this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:28.23,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,There she is! Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:30.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oh wait, no, that was just a falling leaf
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.45,0:03:30.88,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Oopsie!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.06,0:03:34.09,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Well I've heard all I need to, and I'm for one convinced
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:37.52,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,The Bone Stealer is out here and she'll bag us in a cinch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.95,0:03:41.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,She's preying on us ponies, and what she does is wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.34,0:03:44.56,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And she can't be a rumor if she has her own so-ong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:47.77,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,I've met some real bad apples, that'd make the lesser shake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:51.27,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,But she's so diabolical she just might take the cake
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:54.73,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,And if you ain't just lyin', she's evil through and through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.06,0:03:58.06,DEFAULT,,0,0,0,,Somepony needs to stop her now and that's the honest truth
